  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Begin each day with a continental buffet breakfast, with sweet and savoury choices like fresh fruit, pastries, jams, bread, cheeses and cold cuts. There's juices, tea's and coffee too - their silky, foamy, fresh cappuccino's are our favourite! </p>
<p>On half board you'll have dinner at the Restaurant Ciccarelli Esplanade. The chef serves up delicious Tuscan specialties and fresh seafood. You'll have a choice of starter, main and desert - think something like Tunafish “Tataki” browned with thyme, sage, rosemary and pistachio served with sweet and sour onions, followed by beef Tenderloin in “Chianti classico” wine and a tasty tiramisù for pudding. They also have a small menu that caters to vegetarian and vegan diets. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
