  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>are 15m² and equipped with air conditioning, satellite TV, safe, minibar, hairdryer and free wifi. These rooms sleep two people. Rooms with a balcony are available for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>have a balcony and offer more space with 23m², with a small living area. They sleep two people. </p>
<p><strong>Family Suites </strong>are about 23m² and have a balcony. They sleep up to four people and have a double bedroom and a small living area.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are about 45m² and have a balcony with side sea views. They sleep up to four people and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Rooms for Single Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
